snippet.title: Cascadio - Releases May 14th, 2020 - iOS/Android/PC
snippet.description:
Cascadio - a Puzzle of Cascading Sums


https://bakajo.itch.io/cascadio

Cascadio plays like a fast-paced Sudoku.  Arrange cascading flows of numbers to complete this mind bending puzzle of sums.  Unique games are endlessly created and may easily be shared with friends to race for a solution.

https://bakajo.itch.io/cascadio
https://apps.apple.com/us/app/cascadio/id1468989267
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=studio.bakajo.cascadio
